result.title: Day and Night
result.description:
This is my sound postproduction project I've done at school. The task was to create your own soundtrack to a chosen video. I've recorded voices of amateur actors, foleys and chose and edited music and sound effects.

Music used by me in this piece was taken from the features: 

'The Princess Bride' - Mark Knopfler
'Walk The Line' - T Bone Burnett
'La Strada' - Nino Rota

and animations:

'Up' - Michael Giacchino
'Treasure Planet' - James Newton Howard
'Cars' - Randy Newman

I also used a theme from 'Twin Peaks' series by Angelo Badalamenti and some pieces from Paris Music library.
